<%= render 'notifier/email_header' %>
<center class="wrapper" style="display: table;table-layout: fixed;width: 100%;min-width: 620px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;background-color: #fbfbfb">
  <%= render 'notifier/email_logo' %>
  <table class="centered" style="border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0;Margin-left: auto;Margin-right: auto">
    <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="border" style="padding: 0;vertical-align: top;font-size: 1px;line-height: 1px;background-color: #e9e9e9;width: 1px">​</td>
      <td style="padding: 0;vertical-align: top">
        <table class="one-col" style="border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0;Margin-left: auto;Margin-right: auto;width: 600px;background-color: #ffffff;font-size: 14px">
          <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="column" style="padding: 0;vertical-align: top;text-align: left">
              <div>
                <div class="column-top" style="font-size: 32px;line-height: 32px">&nbsp;</div>
              </div>
              <table class="contents" style="border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0;width: 100%">
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="padded" style="padding: 0;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 32px;padding-right: 32px">
                    <p style="Margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: 'Lucida Grande';font-size: 16px;line-height: 25px;Margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: left;">
                      Hey <%= @user.first_name %>,
                    </p>

                    <p style="Margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: 'Lucida Grande';font-size: 16px;line-height: 25px;Margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: left;">

                      Welcome to Meed! We’re excited to have you as a part of our community and to start helping you
                      navigate the (often intimidating) professional world. It's a little overwhelming, we know.
                    </p>

                    <p style="Margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: 'Lucida Grande';font-size: 16px;line-height: 25px;Margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: left;">

                      Back when my co-founder and I were students at USC, we had huge aspirations for our post-grad
                      careers. What we didn't have was the experience to show for it on a traditional resume. We knew we
                      had a lot to offer, but with limited professional experience we were frustrated with how to
                      convey that to potential employers. That's why we founded Meed. </p>

                    <p>

                    <p style="Margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: 'Lucida Grande';font-size: 16px;line-height: 25px;Margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: left;">
                      With Meed, we’ve created a platform where students can participate in an online professional
                      community by displaying projects they’re working on, activities they participate in, and news
                      about industries they are passionate about. By engaging with other students, Meed gives you the
                      opportunity to showcase your interests, talents, and skills to recruiters—even if your resume is
                      still a little sparse. </p>

                    <p style="text-align: center;">
                      <%= link_to 'Let\'s get started', 'https://getmeed.com', :style => 'font-family: "Open Sans", "lucida grande", arial, verdana, "lucida sans unicode", tahoma, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color:#00a651;' %>
                    </p>
                    <p style="Margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: 'Lucida Grande';font-size: 16px;line-height: 25px;Margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: left;">
                     Ravi Vadrevu,
                      <br/>
                      Founder & CEO.
                    </p>


                  </td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>

            </td>
          </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
      <td class="border" style="padding: 0;vertical-align: top;font-size: 1px;line-height: 1px;background-color: #e9e9e9;width: 1px">​</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="spacer" style="font-size: 1px;line-height: 32px;width: 100%">&nbsp;</div>
</center>
<%= render 'notifier/email_footer' %>
</body>
</html>